OL,3,CPlans for new British Sign Language
OL,4,CGCSE move forward following
OL,5,Cconsultation
OL,7,FPlans to offer a British Sign Language
OL,8,FGCSE to pupils have moved forward
OL,9,Fafter the subject content was
OL,10,Ffinalised.
OL,12,FParents, teachers and the deaf and
OL,13,Fhearing communities took part in a 12-
OL,14,Fweek consultation on the content of
OL,15,Fthe British Sign Language (BSL) GCSE.
OL,17,FThe Government is aiming to have exam
OL,18,Fboard syllabuses approved for the new
OL,19,Fqualification from September 2025.
